{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"content":["Place water and 1 tsp of the salt into mixing bowl, insert simmering basket and weigh potatoes into it. Place Varoma dish into position.","Divide green beans into 8 equal bundles and wrap streaky bacon around each bundle. Place bundles into middle of Varoma dish to ensure even steaming and insert Varoma tray.","Place a ramekin onto Varoma tray and add butter, remaining ½ tsp salt and thyme. Secure Varoma lid and steam <b>28 min\/Varoma\/speed 1<b>. Carefully open Varoma to check whether beans and potatoes are cooked through. If not, steam a further <b>2-5 min\/Varoma\/speed 1<b>. Serve green bean bundles with potatoes, drizzled with thyme butter."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"","content":["500 g water","1 ½ tsp salt","600 g potatoes, cut into cubes (3 cm)","200 g fresh green beans","8 - 16 slices streaky bacon (100 g)","80 - 100 g unsalted butter","1 - 2 tsp fresh thyme"]}],"id":"r156349","imageLink":"https:\/\/1.bp.blogspot.com\/-qVGSSuWAp7s\/XZWZuE4xmvI\/AAAAAAAAeRc\/f_qdQ7f_rekBicho8HSJB0LuCdVrNlH-wCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_kcFE_4louiiphSi7.png","title":"Green bean bundles, potatoes and thyme butter","publishedAt":"2017-05-08T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"8 g","fat":"26 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"26 g","calories":"1596 kJ \/ 382 kcal"},"usefulItems":"ramekin","hintsAndTricks":["For a vegetarian version, omit bacon and use spring onion\/shallots or chives to tie the green bean bundles.<br>- Add some chopped garlic to the thyme butter before steaming."],"basicInfo":["easy","20m","50m","4 portions"]}